tool_description: Highly Scalable and Reliable, Organic Google Web Searches (SERP), and at an unbeatable speed.
name: Real-Time Web Search
title: Real-Time Web Search

api_list.name: Search
api_list.description: Get real-time organic search results from across the web. Supports all Google Advanced Search operators such (e.g. inurl:, site:, intitle:, etc).

required_parameters.name: q
required_parameters.description:
Search query.  Supports all Google advanced search operators (*site:*, *inurl:*, *intitle:*, etc).

e.g. `website builder`
e.g. ` site:youtube.com`
e.g. `nda filetype:pdf`
e.g. `cristiano -ronaldo`

optional_parameters.name: limit
optional_parameters.description:
Maximum number of results to return (1-300). 
**Default**: `10`.
